node.text:
MOTORCYCLE GIVEAWAY!

It is with great joy and erect nipples that I am announcing @ruroc & @enginehawk are helping me give away my custom 2015 Kawasaki Ninja 650R AS WELL AS an unreleased Atlas 3.0 helmet AND any jacket of your choice from Ruroc’s new motorcycle gear brand @enginehawk along with some accessories!

How to enter:
• Like and tag three friends
• Make sure you’re following me, @enginehawk & @ruroc
• Repost this on your story for a bonus entry!

The winner will be picked on @enginehawk launch date on April 27th! Good luck boyos! 😁

WARNING - Please be safe and lookout for fake accounts pretending to me, they’re scams.

#giveaway #motorcycle #motorcyclegiveaway #custommotorcyclehelmets #ninja650r #ruroc #enginehawk
